  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "Minimal-profile UnitOfAssurance for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Thirteen credibility factors are assessed under ASME V&V 40-2018. No Context of Use object is attached; intended-use scope is therefore undefined. This package is flagged as a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-ON-01.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-prediction",
